des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in Philadelphia. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Vegan Philadelphia." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Vegan Philadelphia for a fact."
